      "role": "user",
      "content": "I see. It's just hard to tell which side is actually being more \"rational.\" Like, the school says they're just trying to make sure everyone feels safe and included, which sounds pretty objectively good for a learning environment. But then you have these groups saying it's \"indoctrination.\" Is it fair to call those concerns \"legitimate\" when they seem to go against what most medical and educational experts are saying?",
